   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    The sign for "weather" has a few popular versions.
    <br/>
   </p>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    The main version uses "W" hands and moves them both downward using a wavy 
movement. In a way, this is actually an initialized version of the signs for 
"snow" and "rain" which also both move downward.
    <br/>
   </p>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    <br/>
    WEATHER:
    <br/>
    Use a wavy downward movement.
    <br/>
   </p>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    <img border="0" height="216" src="/images/weather1.jpg" width="249"/>
    <img border="0" height="216" src="/images/weather2.jpg" width="249"/>
