    <img border="0" height="216" src="/images/weather4.jpg" width="249"/>
    <img border="0" height="216" src="/images/weather5.jpg" width="249"/>
    <font face="Arial">
     <br/>
     <br/>
     Sample sentence:
Do you like hot weather?
     <br/>
     <br/>
     <br/>
    </font>
    <br/>
   </p>
   <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    <br/>
    Here is another version of weather.  It means the same as the two
handed version.
    <br/>
    Use a wavy downward movement.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <img border="0" height="215" src="/images/weatherb1.jpg" width="217"/>
