    Notes:
    <br/>
    <font face="Arial">
     It isn't as common, but on occasion I'll notice someone using the sign for "wind"
to mean "weather."  I don't recommend doing that. "WIND" is a fine sign 
and great to use for referring to movement of "air" but I just don't see a 
reason to use it as the sign for weather.
     <br/>
    </font>
